## Responsive Typography

Reduce font sizes for mobile to maintain proportions:

```css
/* Desktop */
h1 { font-size: 28px; }
h2 { font-size: 22px; }

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    h1 { font-size: 19px; }
    h2 { font-size: 16px; }
    .form-group label { font-size: 13px; }
}
```

## Spacing Consistency

Reduce all spacing proportionally on mobile:
- Padding: ~30% reduction
- Margins: ~30% reduction
- Gaps: ~25% reduction

This maintains visual hierarchy while fitting more content.
